<p>Hi there 👋</p>

<p>Welcome to Pagecord!</p>
<p>Your blog is live at <a href="<%= blog_home_url(@blog) %>"><%= blog_home_url(@blog) %></a>. To help you get started, here are a few things you can try to personalise your site.</p>

<h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #000000; margin: 28px 0 8px;">🎨 Pick a theme</h3>
<p>Browse the <a href="<%= app_settings_theme_garden_index_url %>">Theme Garden</a> for a ready-made design, then fine-tune it using <a href="https://help.pagecord.com/custom-css">Custom CSS</a> until it's just right.</p>

<h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #000000; margin: 28px 0 8px;">✏️ Make it yours</h3>
<p>Add a Home page, an About page, or anything other page you like. You can even embed posts and tags in pages using <a href="https://help.pagecord.com/dynamic-variables-for-pages">dynamic variables</a>.</p>

<h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #000000; margin: 28px 0 8px;">📮 Post from where you already write</h3>
<p>You can compose posts in the editor, or email a post to <strong><%= @blog.delivery_email %></strong> from <strong><%= @user.email %></strong>. You can even publish from <a href="https://help.pagecord.com/obsidian">Obsidian</a>.</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding-top:12px; padding-bottom:12px;">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <%= link_to "Log in to get started", app_onboarding_url %>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #000000; margin: 28px 0 8px;">🌱 Room to grow</h3>
<p>You can use Pagecord Classic for free, forever. You have a 14-day free trial of the premium features. If you like what you see, subscribe to <a href="<%= app_settings_subscriptions_url %>">Pagecord Premium</a> to connect your own domain name, and send email newsletters to your readers.</p>

<% if @user.marketing_consent %>
  <p>By the way, the <a href="https://blog.pagecord.com">Pagecord blog</a> is itself a Pagecord blog! You're on the mailing list, so look out for regular updates.</p>
<% else %>
  <p>By the way, the <a href="https://blog.pagecord.com">Pagecord blog</a> is itself a Pagecord blog! Subscribe to get regular updates in your inbox or RSS reader.</p>
<% end %>

<p>Stuck, or just want to learn more? Check out <a href="https://help.pagecord.com">the Help Guide</a>, or just reply to this email. I read every one.</p>

